<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Supplier Verification Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f6f6f6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #4CAF50;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 20px;
    }
    .otp {
      display: block;
      width: fit-content;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      color: #888888;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Supplier Verification</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear Supplier,</p>
      <p>{{otp}} is your supplier verification code for registration purposes. Kindly verify and proceed further to add property from your end.</p>
      <p>Thanks,</p>
      <p>The Booking247 Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 Booking247. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>